Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.50,0:01:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.53,0:01:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒支配這座山的\N邪惡帝皇多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.97,0:01:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一邊在各界層\N與多惡達的魔神戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.81,0:01:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊向第七界層前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.14,0:01:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了找出\N種植太好種子的聖地神聖木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.31,0:01:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來到了跑跑村\N在我們面前出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.18,0:01:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘著魔神哈古里昂\N令村民受苦的飛車密斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.58,0:01:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然和密斯用速度比賽\N來分勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但因為虎王也出現了\N所以很大件事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.76,0:02:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,途中把叫出魔神的密斯打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.03,0:02:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比賽只剩下\N我和虎王二人之爭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.03,0:02:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣想的時候\N火美子他們突然出現還勝出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.50,0:02:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們從村民口中\N得知了下個目的地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便是哥羅加地之鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.27,0:02:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.98,0:02:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十五話\N迷你渡的大冒險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.00,0:02:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏露宿很辛苦的\N用這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成帳幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是神奇的折紙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親是折紙的天才呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.05,0:03:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你當猴子真可惜呢\N死河馬!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家快躲起來\N帳幕啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.65,0:03:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,那是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.59,0:03:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來像個工廠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣也好,今天在此露宿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.67,0:03:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是哥羅加地之鄉\N真的在這附近嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.97,0:03:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好去找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向哥羅加地之鄉的占卜師\N哥羅米查問神聖木的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再把這太好種子種下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.01,0:04:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便可以把這第五界層\N恢復原狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.50,0:04:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,幫幫我吧,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.52,0:04:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.36,0:04:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位,我們不是壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.96,0:04:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫戰部渡\N為了打倒多惡達正在旅途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位鄉民停手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打倒多惡達是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.71,0:05:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把創界山的彩虹恢復原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.78,0:05:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有趣又有型的救世主…渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便是我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.29,0:05:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!萬歲!\N和預言一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.00,0:05:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位鄉民,哥羅米說過的\N巨大救世主終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的心意,請吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是真細小呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.91,0:05:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了,師傅\N因為鄉內的人全都很細小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.08,0:05:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你的睡相不好\N差點便把房屋毀掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.09,0:05:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真對不起,我沒想到\N這裏便是哥羅加地之鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.39,0:06:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了不被波格波格工廠\N發現我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.83,0:06:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們便把房子\N裝成石頭的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.43,0:06:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波格波格工廠?\N那是昨天的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.24,0:06:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,是污煙的手下\N新郎子和新娘子的空中工廠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.57,0:06:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們把垃圾丟下來\N把房屋打破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.08,0:06:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我們哥羅加地人\N捉回去當奴隸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真過分呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.35,0:06:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在哥羅米預言的\N巨大救世主出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後便可以安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.42,0:06:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,我們是來找哥羅米的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.03,0:06:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想問她神聖木的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.43,0:06:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥羅米已不在這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.97,0:06:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她被波格波格工廠捉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.47,0:06:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥羅米,快逃吧\N他們快來到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.74,0:06:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺,還差些少\N便可以知道救世主的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.28,0:06:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了鄉民們\N請讓我繼續占吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.10,0:07:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.87,0:07:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知現在會遭到什麼待遇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.91,0:07:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不能原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.48,0:07:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.62,0:07:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點工作,偷懶的話\N我新郎子是不會饒恕你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.46,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快工作!快工作!\N不工作的人我會丟了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們很努力地工作了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要丟我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.11,0:08:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公,接著去洗浴缸\N完了便弄飯給我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.82,0:08:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是用人用到盡\N就算我是入贅女婿也不用…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.92,0:08:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…\N好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.69,0:08:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了\N不可以和他說「好」的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很緊張呢\N會令皺紋增加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.59,0:08:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那是什麼樣子?\N你只在那裏不斷哭便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.59,0:08:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手\N你不用洋蔥我也想哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的未來一定會不幸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.03,0:08:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,我是有未來\N但你卻無未來,我也會占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.00,0:09:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很舒服\N你的眼淚對護膚很有效啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.48,0:09:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這美麗是永恆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.31,0:09:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真嚇了我一跳\N嚇一跳的是我,新娘子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.72,0:09:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出這傢伙然後收拾他\N殘兄弟大人有命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.29,0:09:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要收拾這個渡\N知道了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.83,0:09:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.93,0:09:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論你用什麼方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.91,0:09:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成了\N這邊也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好\N就這樣潛進波格波格工廠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.06,0:09:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是大家坐上這個\N太沒可能了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.63,0:09:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.50,0:10:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們真是沒有我\N便什麼也做不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.77,0:10:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家閉起眼睛吧\N看著也沒關係吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.11,0:10:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行\N真小器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,縮小槌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.46,0:10:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變細小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.29,0:10:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被這個縮小槌打到的話\N什麼也會變小的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.36,0:10:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真厲害呢\N很有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.13,0:10:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等!\N喂!不要開玩笑,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.44,0:10:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,把我變回原狀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.54,0:10:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武一郎先生\N這個法術短期內無法復原的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.95,0:10:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你暫時忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.23,0:10:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒法子,師傅留在這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.13,0:11:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.53,0:11:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了嗎?各位\N隨時可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.70,0:11:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了,3、2、1\N發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.26,0:11:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,先去找哥羅米吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.74,0:11:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等,這次計劃由我定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣也好,先躲起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.92,0:11:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他向這邊來了\N去找哥羅米吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等\N我拜託你不要穿那木屐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行了,向那邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.17,0:12:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是…喂!你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.44,0:12:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘩!是這樣啊!我不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.52,0:13:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫戰部渡\N難道你是哥羅米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.79,0:13:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是來救你的\N來救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我便是你預言中的救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會?錯了\N什麼地方錯了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.87,0:13:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來救我的是巨大的救世主\N不是像你們這般細小的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無禮的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.84,0:13:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大猩猩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.71,0:13:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是大猩猩啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.32,0:13:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,他其實是猴子\N對,猴子…不對!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.72,0:13:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原因之後再說\N首先是要離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.16,0:13:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃得很飽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.50,0:13:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蛋…蛋樣啊!混帳!\N你這個哥羅加地人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.40,0:13:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有其他在嗎?混蛋\N我要一個不留地捉住你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了!\N發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.52,0:14:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!到此為止了\N我做你的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.69,0:14:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.96,0:14:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我也做你對手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.36,0:14:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好?好?好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.27,0:14:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔瘋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.45,0:14:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥羅米,沒事嗎?\N總之先逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.56,0:15:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你便是渡嗎?竟自己送上門\N真是蠢材,讓我踩扁你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.84,0:15:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.85,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去工廠後面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.38,0:15:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位趕快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.86,0:15:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會讓你逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.40,0:15:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,我只要你一個便夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要小看我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.12,0:15:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!\N可惡!快回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.69,0:16:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很巨型!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎辦好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.78,0:16:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!這邊啊,我用槌子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.72,0:16:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把你鑽得全身是洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.63,0:17:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,變小了的我\N力量也變弱了,你要注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了,去吧!龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.51,0:17:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親,叫幻神丸出來啊\N幻神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.90,0:17:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很大呢\N結果還是由我控制呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.55,0:18:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是壞的老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.75,0:18:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,我果然很聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得好,渡\N是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.83,0:18:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.13,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了,就算是我\N這麼高掉下去也會粉碎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.38,0:18:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,恢復原來的太小了\N可以變成龍王丸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.85,0:18:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!\N力量全開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.73,0:18:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變身!龍王丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變形!鳳凰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變形!龍王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.71,0:19:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的小鬼,這樣我也怒了\N老公,合體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.39,0:19:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合體魔神,鋼鐵巨鑽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.10,0:20:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來一個\N中計了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.34,0:20:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,斬斷電線吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.93,0:20:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常重呢\N被他這樣壓著我動不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個大嬸非常超重呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.74,0:20:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒有弱點嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.97,0:20:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新郎子因為被新娘子\N欺負得很慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一聽到「好」便會失常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.41,0:20:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.75,0:20:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝負現在才開始,好!來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.32,0:20:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!你不來的話我便來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.96,0:20:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!好!好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.73,0:21:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,拔劍吧!\N好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.95,0:21:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.03,0:21:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太大意了\N對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.17,0:21:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.88,0:21:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占卜指示\N聖地神聖木在飛龍鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.18,0:21:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛龍鎮嗎?\N謝謝你,哥羅米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.39,0:22:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祈求你一路平安\N巨大的救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.92,0:22:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!向飛龍鎮出發吧

